718
00:33:05,870 --> 00:33:07,660
We're in different positions,

719
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,510
and we have different resources.

720
00:33:10,130 --> 00:33:12,550
But from a personal perspective,

721
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:14,670
I think you want to come back.

722
00:33:15,190 --> 00:33:17,420
