723
00:33:18,410 --> 00:33:19,830
The lawsuit is ongoing.

724
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,370
There's constant online criticism.

725
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:23,230
And competitors have added insult to injury.

726
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:24,440
Moreover,

727
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:27,430
