728
00:33:30,390 --> 00:33:31,540
So you mean...

729
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:34,200
I shouldn't come back, right?

730
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:35,640
Then tell me,

731
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:38,030
