00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,950
The flavor is not the same as this.

869
00:40:52,750 --> 00:40:53,540
That's true.

870
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:56,440
You didn't...

871
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:59,130
come back just because of this, did you?

872
00:41:00,270 --> 00:41:01,510
What on earth happened?

873
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:04,420
Uncle.

874
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:06,590
Did you take your medicine this morning?

875
00:41:06,610 --> 00:41:07,390
Don't change the topic.

876
00:41:07,530 --> 00:41:08,830
You didn't take it, did you?

877
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:12,830
Look at you.

878
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:15,750
Alright.

879
00:41:15,750 --> 00:41:16,750
I know what I'm doing.

880
00:41:16,870 --> 00:41:18,490
You haven't even taken your pre-breakfast dose.

881
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:20,030
Can't I take it after breakfast?

882
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:20,990
But the doctor said you need

883
00:41:20,990 --> 00:41:21,950
to take medicine

884
00:41:21,950 --> 00:41:22,630
before breakfast,

885
00:41:22,010 --> 00:41:23,270
[Before breakfast]
[After breakfast]
[Noon]
[Evening]
[Before bed]

886
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:24,550
after breakfast, at noon, in the evening, and before bed.

887
00:41:25,550 --> 00:41:27,660
Sis knew you wouldn't take your medicine on time.

888
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,200
I can't believe you kids.

889
00:41:32,230 --> 00:41:33,230
You just

890
00:41:33,370 --> 00:41:34,820
have everything backwards,

891
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:38,450
trying to tell an old man what to do.

892
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:40,150
If this were in the past, girls like you

893
00:41:40,170 --> 00:41:42,060
wouldn't be able to find a husband

894
00:41:42,270 --> 00:41:44,300
because they valued the Three Obediences and Four Virtues.

895
00:41:47,450 --> 00:41:48,600
Uncle Xie,

896
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:51,060
what we're doing is called respecting the elderly and protecting the young.

897
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,230
We care about our elders.

898
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:54,230
We're looking out for your health.

899
00:41:59,450 --> 00:42:00,410
I've taken it.

900
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:06,010
You still haven't answered my question.

901
00:42:06,550 --> 00:42:08,310
You came back from abroad.

902
00:42:08,540 --> 00:42:09,790
If your mother finds out

903
00:42:09,790 --> 00:42:11,750
Linhui and I have been hiding it from her,

904
00:42:11,750 --> 00:42:13,270
the consequences will be very serious.

905
00:42:13,290 --> 00:42:14,900
With her temper, if she makes a fuss,

906
00:42:15,010 --> 00:42:17,030
it's not something an ordinary person can handle.

907
00:42:18,190 --> 00:42:19,750
What are your plans for the future?

908
00:42:22,710 --> 00:42:23,310
I'm done eating.

909
00:42:23,310 --> 00:42:24,150
I'm going upstairs first.

910
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:25,270
I haven't finished my words yet!

911
00:42:25,350 --> 00:42:26,470
Save it for next time.

912
00:42:26,470 --> 00:42:27,270
We'll talk later.

913
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,230
Bye bye.

914
00:42:34,790 --> 00:42:35,950
I did buy too much.

915
00:42:36,750 --> 00:42:37,910
It's even enough for dinner.

916
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:40,530
Eat.

917
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:48,600
Who is it?

918
00:42:50,820 --> 00:42:51,700
Coming.

919
00:42:56,780 --> 00:42:58,220
It's... It's you.

920
00:42:58,930 --> 00:43:00,050
Long time no see,

921
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:01,180
Xie.
